page.title: 11MY TYPICAL DAY
page.content: A typical day for me would be to get up at 6.45am .When I'm up I make my bed, then I get dressed. At about 7.15am I go downstairs and have my bowl of either Cocoa Pops or Rice Krispies. At 7.30am I brush my teeth and wash my face. After that I put my coat on and get my bag ready and wait for my friend to call for me to walk to school. When we get to school we play a game in the playground before doing our work. At 10.20 we have our assembly which is followed by a short playtime which ends at 11.00. We work for one hour, then we have dinner then we have a playtime until 1.10pm. We work solid until 3.10pm after that we have 5 minutes of story then at 3.15pm we go home. At the end of the day I will go to bed at 9.30pm.
